description: Record to support submission of GeneRIFs for a gene not in Gene (Agrobacterium genomic group 1; Agrobacterium genomic species 1; Agrobacterium genomic species G1; Agrobacterium genomosp. 1; Agrobacterium tumefaciens genomovar G1; Rhizobium lupini H13-3.  Use when strain, subtype, isolate, etc. is unspecified, or when different from all specified ones in Gene.).
